data.name: AccessibleEventObject
data.desc:
this struct describes an accessible event, that is broadcasted from the XAccessibleEventBroadcaster and notified to XAccessibleEventListener.

It is usually implemented by AccessibleContext.

**Since**

    OOo 1.1.2

items.name: EventId
lines: specifies the type of this event.
For a list of possible events see AccessibleEventId.

items.name: NewValue
lines: for events that specifies a value change, this is the new value.
Depending on the EventId, this can be void.

items.name: OldValue
lines: for events that specifies a value change, this is the old value.
Depending on the EventId, this can be void.
